dct_description_sm: This polygon shapefile contains the boundaries of GIS zones referenced in other energy-related datasets produced by Hart Energy Publishing (Rextag). This layer is from the summer quarter update of 2014.
This dataset may be used for viewing, querying, or to provide a basemap to support analysis with other data from this collection.
This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
